concern I have.

03:54.602 --> 03:57.836
[jeff] yeah, well...
I think it's a gamble. But...

03:57.938 --> 03:59.705
-[shane speaking]
-your brother here
is a gambling man.

03:59.707 --> 04:01.239
That's how fishing is.

04:01.241 --> 04:04.543
-[shane speaking]
-[jeff] every day you go
out fishing, it's a gamble.

04:04.645 --> 04:07.212
[josh] right now,
we need a hail mary like
you wouldn't believe.

04:07.214 --> 04:08.847
Time is ticking.

04:08.916 --> 04:10.515
This hopefully this works out.

04:13.020 --> 04:14.219
All right, sounds good.

04:14.221 --> 04:15.420
[josh] what do you say? Cool.

04:15.422 --> 04:16.822
-[casey] is it a plan?
-It's a plan. Okay.

04:16.824 --> 04:18.056
Sounds good.

