04:39.013 --> 04:40.912
<i> Times like</i>
<i> this when I have no idea</i>

04:40.914 --> 04:43.115
<i> If my business</i>
<i> is going to survive,</i>

04:43.117 --> 04:47.119
That's when I realize
what the old man went
through day-in and day-out.

04:48.555 --> 04:50.255
Geez, you go through
a couple of marriages,

04:50.291 --> 04:53.158
You smoke cigarettes like
