for other people's families.

21:11.604 --> 21:14.605
You know, it's... It's hard.

21:14.607 --> 21:16.440
[nelson] but that was
your father's dream. Yeah?

21:16.509 --> 21:18.042
My father's dream, yeah.

21:20.013 --> 21:24.949
I appreciate this
and I've learned a lot
about your guys industry,

21:25.051 --> 21:26.817
Catch fish,
respect on the ocean.

21:26.819 --> 21:28.519
[nelson nodding head]

21:28.521 --> 21:29.954
So, what do you think,
you know?

21:29.956 --> 21:31.322
Can I call on you for help?

21:38.865 --> 21:42.300
If we ever needed help,
you know,
just for information.

21:43.603 --> 21:46.237
Now, do you think
you can help us?

21:46.339 --> 21:49.407
<i> Our weekly order's coming u</i>
<i> pretty quick.</i>

21:49.409 --> 21:51.509
<i> So, jeff brought me</i>
<i> to his hometown,</i>

21:51.511 --> 21:56.647
