fishing network.

21:56.749 --> 21:57.782
So, what do you think?

21:57.784 --> 21:59.617
You know,
can I call on you for help?

22:02.855 --> 22:06.857
Honestly, it took me 55 years

22:08.361 --> 22:10.728
To realize what family
was all about, yeah.

22:11.931 --> 22:14.065
I follow your story.

22:14.100 --> 22:19.804
Your dad had on a history
