the person he is, you know.

22:19.806 --> 22:21.405
And he only was handing
it down to you.

22:21.407 --> 22:22.606
[josh] yeah.

22:22.608 --> 22:26.043
Same like for me,
same like for jeff.
You know?

22:27.847 --> 22:30.047
